Thank you for your reply. 

About the role
We are looking for an experienced Tech Lead who combines strong Solidity engineering skills with leadership and communication ability.

Position Type : Full-time / Part-time
Work Location : On-site / Remote (Flexible)
Compensation : $50-$100 per hour initially (based on experience and skills)

Responsibilities
• Lead Blockchain Development, ensuring code quality, scalability, and performance.
• Review Solidity code for security, gas efficiency, and readability.
• Collaborate with frontend, QA, and product teams to deliver production-grade dApps and backend services.

Requirements
• 3+ years of professional software development experience in Solidity
• Deep understanding of the Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM).
• Proven experience building and deploying 1+ blockchain-based platforms with cross-functional teams.
• Strong understanding of gas optimization, storage layout, and low-level opcodes.
• Fluency in English (written and spoken).

Nice to Have
• Experience with gRPC / REST API integrations.
• Knowledge of Zero-Knowledge (ZK) tools — Circom, SnarkJS.
• Familiarity with audit tools like Slither, MythX, or Echidna.
• Ability to read and analyze external smart contracts (DeFi, NFT, or DAO).

You will go through three steps in our hiring process:
• Technical Assignment - to evaluate your Solidity skills and overall blockchain knowledge.
• Technical Interview with the CTO - to discuss your technical approach, architecture understanding, and problem-solving style.
• Final Interview with the CEO - to align on vision, culture, and leadership fit.

If you successfully pass all three steps, you’ll join our team!

Benefits
• Remote work allowance, training & certification support
• Book/IT equipment purchase subsidy
• Side jobs OK, stock option plan
• Generous leave policy (summer, holidays, personal days)

If you want to join a team that builds meaningful products with the potential to change the world, submit your proposal now!
Joining us will open up exciting opportunities for you.


